---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---
<Base title="Qiqihar — New Castle International Corp.">
  <Nav />

  <section class="page-hero" style="background-image:linear-gradient(to bottom,rgba(13,31,60,.7),rgba(13,31,60,.95)),url('/images/qiqihar-city.png');background-size:cover;background-position:center">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">Qiqihar, China</div>
      <h1>Our Partner City.<br><em>An Open Invitation.</em></h1>
      <p class="sub">New Castle County and Qiqihar have been formally linked since November 2014 — when NCIC brought both governments to the table and made history as the first county-level US-China sister city agreement in Delaware. A decade later, we're ready to build on what we started.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="qiq-intro">
    <div class="container two-col">
      <div>
        <div class="section-label">About Qiqihar</div>
        <h2>A City of 6 Million.<br>A Partner Worth Knowing.</h2>
        <p>Qiqihar is a prefecture-level city in Heilongjiang Province in northeastern China — the second-largest city in the province and one of the most important industrial and agricultural centers in the country.</p>
        <p>Designated by China as the "Capital of Organic Food" and "The Machinery City," Qiqihar is a study in productive contradiction — ancient garrison city turned modern industrial powerhouse, with a food production ecosystem that feeds much of China.</p>
        <p>NCIC has direct relationships with Qiqihar's government and business community, built over two years of in-person meetings, delegation exchanges, and a signed bilateral agreement that is still in effect today. We know this city, its people, and its ambitions. And we believe the best chapter of this partnership is still ahead.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="qiq-stats">
          <div class="qstat"><span>~6M</span><span>Population</span></div>
          <div class="qstat"><span>$20B+</span><span>GDP</span></div>
          <div class="qstat"><span>#1</span><span>Capital of Organic Food in China</span></div>
          <div class="qstat"><span>1,200+</span><span>Food Manufacturing Companies</span></div>
          <div class="qstat"><span>2014</span><span>Sister City Agreement with NCC</span></div>
          <div class="qstat"><span>Active</span><span>Agreement Still in Force</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="qiq-industries">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">What Qiqihar Produces</div>
      <h2>Industrial Strengths &amp; Export Opportunities</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">Qiqihar's economy spans heavy industry, organic agriculture, and food processing — creating direct complementary opportunities with New Castle County's logistics, financial services, and consumer market access.</p>
      <div class="ind-grid">
        <div class="ind-card">
          <div class="ind-icon">🌾</div>
          <h3>Organic Food &amp; Agriculture</h3>
          <p>China's designated Organic Food Capital. Over 1,200 food manufacturing companies. Major producers of organic grains, soybeans, dairy, and specialty foods. Mengniu dairy — one of China's largest — has manufacturing presence in Qiqihar.</p>
          <div class="ind-match">US Match: Port of Wilmington cold chain logistics, Delaware food processing infrastructure, Northeast consumer market access</div>
        </div>
        <div class="ind-card">
          <div class="ind-icon">⚙️</div>
          <h3>Heavy Machinery &amp; Equipment</h3>
          <p>Qiqihar is "The Machinery City" — a major producer of heavy machinery, railroad equipment, rolling stock, machine tools, diesel engines, and cranes. Home to major state-owned enterprises in industrial manufacturing.</p>
          <div class="ind-match">US Match: Infrastructure development projects, port equipment needs, advanced manufacturing partnerships</div>
        </div>
        <div class="ind-card">
          <div class="ind-icon">🥛</div>
          <h3>Dairy &amp; Food Processing</h3>
          <p>The Nen River plain surrounding Qiqihar is one of China's premier dairy farming districts. Significant production of milk powder and dairy products. Sugar refining from local sugar beets. Major food processing infrastructure.</p>
          <div class="ind-match">US Match: American dairy technology and equipment, cold storage expertise, USDA-compliant processing partnerships</div>
        </div>
        <div class="ind-card">
          <div class="ind-icon">🌲</div>
          <h3>Timber &amp; Wood Products</h3>
          <p>Access to timber from the Da Hinggan (Greater Khingan) Range — one of China's largest forested areas. Large woodworking sector and paper production.</p>
          <div class="ind-match">US Match: Delaware construction sector, Wilmington building materials market</div>
        </div>
        <div class="ind-card">
          <div class="ind-icon">🏭</div>
          <h3>Textiles &amp; Electronics</h3>
          <p>Diversified industrial base including textile manufacturing and electronics production. Growing light manufacturing sector alongside traditional heavy industry.</p>
          <div class="ind-match">US Match: American retail distribution, Northeast consumer market entry</div>
        </div>
        <div class="ind-card">
          <div class="ind-icon">🍶</div>
          <h3>Consumer Goods &amp; Beverages</h3>
          <p>Alcohol manufacturing and consumer goods companies actively seeking US distribution partners. Chinese consumer brands with interest in establishing American market presence.</p>
          <div class="ind-match">US Match: Delaware LLC structure for US market entry, Philadelphia-area distribution networks, retail partnerships</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="our-history">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">Our Shared History</div>
      <h2>What We Built Together</h2>
      <div class="history-photos">
        <div class="hp-item">
          <img src="/images/gallery/agreement-signing.jpg" alt="Agreement signing" />
          <div class="hp-cap">November 2014 — Official Sister City Agreement Signed</div>
        </div>
        <div class="hp-item">
          <img src="/images/gallery/boardroom-full.jpg" alt="Boardroom meeting" />
          <div class="hp-cap">2016 — Joint Economic Development Summit, NCC Government Center</div>
        </div>
        <div class="hp-item">
          <img src="/images/gallery/delegation-dinner.jpg" alt="Delegation dinner" />
          <div class="hp-cap">2016 — Delegation Dinner with Chinese Corporate Leaders</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="history-text">
        <p>The NCC-Qiqihar relationship was built through years of patient relationship-building — not government grant programs or formal diplomatic channels. NCIC principals traveled to China, hosted delegations in Delaware, coordinated meetings between Chinese corporate executives and Delaware officials, and navigated the complex cultural and political landscape on both sides.</p>
        <p>The result was the only county-level US-China sister city agreement in Delaware — a formal bilateral framework covering economy, trade, science, technology, culture, education, sports, and tourism. That agreement is still on the books. The relationship is ready to be reactivated.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="invitation">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="inv-inner">
        <div class="section-label" style="color:var(--gold)">A Direct Message</div>
        <h2>To Our Friends in Qiqihar</h2>
        <div class="inv-text">
          <p>We haven't forgotten what we built together. The agreement we signed in 2014 was just the beginning — and the work that followed, the meetings, the delegation visits, the conversations about port investment and education exchange and organic food distribution, showed us what this partnership could be.</p>
          <p>New Castle County has new leadership. The region has matured. And NCIC is back — with a clearer vision, a stronger platform, and a genuine desire to finish what we started.</p>
          <p>We are actively inviting Qiqihar's government, businesses, and educational institutions to reconnect. The education exchange programs we discussed. The organic food distribution opportunities. The investment pathways into the American market. All of it remains on the table.</p>
          <p>If you are reading this in Qiqihar — in government, in business, in a school or university — we would like to hear from you. NCIC is ready to work.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="/partner" class="gold-btn-large">Reconnect With NCIC →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="qiq-maps">
    <div class="container maps-grid">
      <div>
        <img src="/images/china-map.png" alt="Qiqihar location in China" style="width:100%;display:block" />
        <div class="map-cap">Qiqihar — Heilongjiang Province, Northeast China</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <img src="/images/world-map.png" alt="Delaware to Qiqihar" style="width:100%;display:block" />
        <div class="map-cap">New Castle County, Delaware ↔ Qiqihar, China</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Base>

<style>
.page-hero{padding:80px 0;border-bottom:2px solid var(--gold);color:var(--offwhite)}
.page-hero h1{font-size:clamp(28px,4vw,52px);font-weight:normal;margin-bottom:20px;line-height:1.1}
.page-hero h1 em{font-style:normal;color:var(--gold)}
.page-hero .sub{font-family:'Arial',sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#94A3B8;max-width:660px;line-height:1.8}
.qiq-intro{padding:80px 0;background:var(--offwhite)}
.two-col{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:64px;align-items:start}
.qiq-intro h2{font-size:clamp(24px,3vw,36px);color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:20px;font-weight:normal;line-height:1.2}
.qiq-intro p{font-family:'Arial',sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:16px}
.qiq-stats{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:2px;background:var(--light)}
.qstat{background:var(--offwhite);padding:24px;text-align:center}
.qstat span:first-child{display:block;font-size:clamp(20px,2.5vw,28px);color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:6px}
.qstat span:last-child{font-family:'Arial',sans-serif;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted)}
.qiq-industries{padding:80px 0;background:var(--light)}
.qiq-industries h2{font-size:clamp(24px,3vw,36px);color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:16px;font-weight:normal}
.section-intro{font-family:'Arial',sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:var(--muted);max-width:640px;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:48px}
.ind-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:2px;background:#D0C9BC}
.ind-card{background:var(--offwhite);padding:28px}
.ind-icon{font-size:28px;display:block;margin-bottom:14px}
.ind-card h3{font-size:16px;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:10px;font-weight:normal}
.ind-card p{font-family:'Arial',sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:16px}
.ind-match{font-family:'Arial',sans-serif;font-size:11px;color:var(--navy);background:var(--light);padding:10px 12px;border-left:2px solid var(--gold);line-height:1.5}
.our-history{padding:80px 0;background:var(--navy);color:var(--offwhite)}
.our-history h2{font-size:clamp(24px,3vw,36px);color:var(--offwhite);margin-bottom:40px;font-weight:normal}
.history-photos{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:3px;margin-bottom:40px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.05)}
.hp-item img{width:100%;height:200px;object-fit:cover;display:block}
.hp-cap{font-family:'Arial',sans-serif;font-size:11px;color:#64748B;padding:10px 0;letter-spacing:.03em}
.history-text p{font-family:'Arial',sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#94A3B8;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:16px;max-width:800px}
.invitation{padding:80px 0;background:var(--offwhite)}
.inv-inner{max-width:780px;margin:0 auto;text-align:center}
.invitation h2{font-size:clamp(26px,3vw,40px);color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:32px;font-weight:normal}
.inv-text p{font-family:'Arial',sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.9;margin-bottom:20px;text-align:left}
.gold-btn-large{display:inline-block;background:var(--navy);color:var(--offwhite);padding:20px 48px;font-family:'Arial',sans-serif;font-size:12px;letter-spacing:.25em;text-transform:uppercase;text-decoration:none;margin-top:32px;transition:background .2s}
.gold-btn-large:hover{background:var(--slate)}
.qiq-maps{padding:64px 0;background:var(--light)}
.maps-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:40px}
.map-cap{font-family:'Arial',sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);text-align:center;padding-top:12px;letter-spacing:.05em}
@media(max-width:900px){.two-col,.ind-grid,.history-photos,.maps-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:2px}}
@media(max-width:768px){.qiq-intro,.qiq-industries,.our-history,.invitation,.qiq-maps{padding:56px 0}}
</style>
